<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Internal Contractor Management System</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            color: #1f2933;
        }

        .top-bar {
            background-color: #0f4c81;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 18px 40px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .top-sub {
            background-color: #e8f1fb;
            padding: 10px 40px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #334e68;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d0dce7;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .description {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4a5d73;
            max-width: 950px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dce3ec;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 22px;
            transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #102a43;
        }

        .card-desc {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #5c6f82;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7c93;
            border-top: 1px solid #dce3ec;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top-bar">
    Internal Contractor Management System
</div>

<div class="top-sub">
    Secure internal platform for requirement management, technical evaluation, and governance
</div>

<div class="container">

    <div class="section-title">Overview</div>
    <div class="description">
        This application is designed to support the complete internal workflow for contractor
        and technical hiring. It enables structured requirement submission, standardized interview
        feedback, lifecycle tracking, and compliance documentation for engineering roles.
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">System Modules</div>

    <div class="cards">

        <a href="requirement_request.html">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">Requirement Request Application</div>
                <div class="card-desc">
                    Used by hiring managers to raise and document new requirements including role scope,
                    skill expectations, experience levels, and priority.
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="interview_feedback.html">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">Interview Feedback Form</div>
                <div class="card-desc">
                    Enables interviewers to submit structured technical feedback covering design
                    verification, physical design, chip manufacturing concepts, and overall assessment.
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="requirement_lifecycle.html">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">Requirement Lifecycle & Traceability</div>
                <div class="card-desc">
                    Provides visibility into the current status of requirements across review,
                    interview, feedback, approval, and closure stages.
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="evaluation_compliance.html">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">Evaluation & Compliance</div>
                <div class="card-desc">
                    Ensures standardized evaluation practices, governance controls,
                    documentation consistency, and audit readiness.
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

    </div>

</div>

<div class="footer">
    Internal Use Only | Confidential | Contractor Management Platform
</div>

</body>
</html>
